data.description: Welcome to your future home, a charming residence with endless potential! Cosmetic updates needed. This concrete block gem, awaits new owners to add their personal touch. With its classic design and sturdy structure, this property is an ideal canvas for cosmetic updates, making it a perfect starter home or lucrative rental investment. Step inside to discover original hardwood floors  throughout the living spaces. The roof and AC were both upgraded in 2017. A fully fenced, generously sized yard provides privacy. A covered carport and additional parking on the side ensure convenience for you and your guests.
